01:54:28.700 --> 01:54:34.220
[Amit Varma]: or offline and please pick up Malevolent Republic by Kapil Komireddy. Tons of thought provoking

01:54:34.220 --> 01:54:42.420
[Amit Varma]: insights there and absolutely fabulous prose. You can follow Kapil on Twitter at Kapskom.

